<p>Now we're close! Inside, add an if statement: if <code>$event-&gt;getData()</code>:This form is
always bound to a <code>GenusScientist</code> object. So this will return the <code>GenusScientist</code>
object bound to this form, <em>or</em> - if this is a new form - then it may return <code>null</code>.
That's why we'll say if <code>$event-&gt;getData() &amp;&amp; $event-&gt;getData()-&gt;getId()</code>:</p>
