<p>In human-speak: as long as there is a <code>GenusScientist</code> bound to this form and it's been
saved to the database - i.e. it has an id value - then let's unset the <code>user</code> field
from the form.</p>
<p>To do that, fetch the form with <code>$form = $event-&gt;getForm()</code>. Then, literally,
<code>unset($form['user'])</code>:</p>
