<p>Else, use a strong tag and print the user's e-mail address with <code>genusScientistForm.vars</code> -
which is something we mastered in our <a href="https://knpuniversity.com/screencast/symfony-form-theming/i-heart-form-variables">Form Theming tutorial</a> -
<code>.data</code> - which will be a <code>GenusScientist</code> object - <code>.user.email</code>:</p>
