<p>This says: find the <code>GenusScientist</code> object behind this form, call <code>getUser()</code> on
it, and then call <code>getEmail()</code> on that.</p>
<p>I think it's time to celebrate! Refresh the form. It looks <em>exactly</em> like I wanted.
It's like my birthday! And when we add a new one, it <em>still</em> has the drop-down.
You guys are the best!</p>

    
